Titolo: The Three Stooges (video game)

Anno: 1987

Descrizione: The Three Stooges is a video game released by Cinemaware in 1987 for the Amiga based on the comedy trio of the same name. Players control Stooges Moe, Larry, and Curly in minigames based on Stooges films with the aim of raising enough money to save an orphanage. It was ported to the Apple IIGS, Atari ST, Commodore 64, MS-DOS, NES and Game Boy Advance. The game has been praised as a faithful adaptation of the Stooges films, but has been criticized for repetitive gameplay and limited replay value.
A remake was released for Microsoft Windows and Macintosh.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
